<h2>Blazor WebAssembly by Example</h2>
<h3>Chapter 6</h3>
This project includes the following pages:
<ul>
    <li><b>Home</b>: This page.</li>
    <li><b>Load Model</b>: Loads the ONNX model and initializes the session.</li>       
    <li><b>Run Inference</b>: Runs inference on the model with sample input and displays the output.</li>           
    <li><b>Test Compare</b>: A simple interface to compare two text inputs and display their similarity score.</li>
</ul>
